opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 11th day of December, 2014, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus and the Motion for Bail are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
